value.0:
--------------------------------------------------------
Storing Items
--------------------------------------------------------
Put your item in the deposit box. On closing you will receive a receipt for it as long as you have less than 20 items stored for your character and the item is not a plot item, gold, or a bag/box. You can store one item at a time, extra items in the box are ignored. The box will be locked for 5 seconds after closing the lid.

Don't forget to take any remaining items out of the box!

--------------------------------------------------------
Retreiving Items
--------------------------------------------------------
You put your receipt in the retreive box. On closing you will receive the relevant item. You will also be charged a fee of 5 gold pieces. The box will be locked for 3 seconds after closing the lid.

--------------------------------------------------------
Transport
--------------------------------------------------------
You can collect your items in a another office than the one you stored the item in. You will have to pay an extra fee of 20 gold for the transport.

--------------------------------------------------------
Quota
--------------------------------------------------------
You can store up to 20 items with a single character. Mind that if you give a receipt to somebody else the item stored with it still counts against your balance. It's therefore advised to exchange items, not receipts.
